'''2X-7KPR ("Tooex")''' was a [[Color/Legends|green]] domed [[KPR security droid/Legends|KPR security droid]] operational during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was capable of monitoring floodlights and [[Perimeter sensor/Legends|perimeter sensors]] as well as maintaining security devices. The [[Droid/Legends|droid]] was originally owned by [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] until it was stolen,<ref name="CCG" /> ending up in the possession of the [[Jawa/Legends|Jawa]] [[Nebit's tribe/Legends|tribe]] led by [[Nebit/Legends|Nebit]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].<ref name="VG">{{SWArchive|url=episode-iv/explore/visualguides/chp08.html|text=Visual Guide &mdash; Chapter 8: Droids for Sale}}</ref>

In [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]],<ref name="TEC">''[[The Essential Chronology (real-world book)|The Essential Chronology]]'' dates the events of {{Film|IV}} to [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].</ref> Nebit's tribe stopped at the [[Lars homestead/Legends|Lars homestead]].<ref name="ANH">{{Film|IV}}</ref> Though the droid's [[Sensor/Legends|sensor]] package still worked at the time, its [[tread]]s were faulty and needed the Jawas help to move.<ref name="VG" /> 2X-7KPR was offered for sale to the [[Moisture farmer/Legends|moisture farmer]] [[Owen Lars/Legends|Owen Lars]]. Lars passed on 2X-7KPR, eventually settling on the purchase of [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]].<ref name="ANH">{{Film|IV}}</ref>

